Selected Answer: C
to output returned values from a child module to CLI - Declare the output in both the root and child module. For example:

child-module.tf

output "child_foo" {
 value = "foobar"
}

main.tf

module "child" {
 source = "path/to/child"
}

output "output_to_cli" {
 value = module.child.child_foo
}
